<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SmartAgro - Análise Blockchain para o Agronegócio</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
      :root {
          --primary: #2E7D32;
          --primary-dark: #1B5E20;
          --primary-light: #4CAF50;
          --secondary: #FF9800;
          --accent: #2196F3;
          --text: #333333;
          --text-light: #666666;
          --background: #F5F5F5;
          --white: #FFFFFF;
          --shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
          --transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      
      * {
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
          box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      
      body {
          font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
          background-color: var(--background);
          color: var(--text);
          line-height: 1.6;
      }
      
      .container {
          max-width: 1200px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          padding: 0 20px;
      }
      
      /* Header */
      header {
          background-color: var(--white);
          box-shadow: var(--shadow);
          position: sticky;
          top: 0;
          z-index: 100;
      }
      
      .header-content {
          display: flex;
          justify-content: space-between;
          align-items: center;
          padding: 15px 0;
      }
      
      .logo {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 12px;
      }
      
      .logo-icon {
          color: var(--primary);
          font-size: 28px;
      }
      
      .logo-text {
          font-size: 24px;
          font-weight: 700;
          color: var(--primary);
      }
      
      .logo-subtitle {
          font-size: 14px;
          color: var(--text-light);
          margin-top: -4px;
      }
      
      .user-info {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 10px;
      }
      
      .user-avatar {
          width: 40px;
          height: 40px;
          border-radius: 50%;
          background-color: var(--primary-light);
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          color: white;
          font-weight: bold;
      }
      
      /* Hero Section */
      .hero {
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
          color: white;
          padding: 60px 0;
          margin-bottom: 40px;
      }
      
      .hero-content {
          max-width: 800px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          text-align: center;
      }
      
      .hero h1 {
          font-size: 36px;
          margin-bottom: 16px;
          font-weight: 700;
      }
      
      .hero p {
          font-size: 18px;
          opacity: 0.9;
          margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      
      .workflow-steps {
          display: flex;
          justify-content: center;
          gap: 30px;
          margin-top: 30px;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      
      .step {
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
          max-width: 150px;
      }
      
      .step-number {
          width: 40px;
          height: 40px;
          border-radius: 50%;
          background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          margin-bottom: 10px;
          font-weight: bold;
      }
      
      .step-text {
          font-size: 14px;
          text-align: center;
          opacity: 0.9;
      }
      
      /* Cards Section */
      .cards-section {
          padding: 40px 0 80px;
      }
      
      .section-title {
          text-align: center;
          margin-bottom: 40px;
          font-size: 28px;
          color: var(--text);
          position: relative;
      }
      
      .section-title::after {
          content: '';
          display: block;
          width: 80px;
          height: 4px;
          background-color: var(--primary);
          margin: 12px auto 0;
          border-radius: 2px;
      }
      
      .cards-grid {
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
          gap: 24px;
      }
      
      .card {
          background-color: var(--white);
          border-radius: 12px;
          overflow: hidden;
          box-shadow: var(--shadow);
          transition: var(--transition);
          cursor: pointer;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          height: 100%;
      }
      
      .card:hover {
          transform: translateY(-8px);
          box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
      }
      
      .card-icon {
          color: white;
          font-size: 28px;
          padding: 24px;
          display: flex;
          justify-content: center;
          align-items: center;
      }
      
      .card-1 .card-icon {
          background-color: var(--accent);
      }
      
      .card-2 .card-icon {
          background-color: var(--secondary);
      }
      
      .card-3 .card-icon {
          background-color: var(--primary);
      }
      
      .card-4 .card-icon {
          background-color: #9C27B0;
      }
      
      .card-content {
          padding: 24px;
          flex-grow: 1;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
      }
      
      .card-title {
          font-size: 20px;
          margin-bottom: 12px;
          color: var(--text);
      }
      
      .card-description {
          color: var(--text-light);
          margin-bottom: 20px;
          flex-grow: 1;
      }
      
      .card-button {
          background-color: var(--primary);
          color: white;
          border: none;
          padding: 12px 20px;
          border-radius: 6px;
          font-weight: 600;
          cursor: pointer;
          transition: var(--transition);
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          gap: 8px;
      }
      
      .card-button:hover {
          background-color: var(--primary-dark);
      }
      
      /* Footer */
      footer {
          background-color: var(--white);
          padding: 40px 0;
          border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
      
      .footer-content {
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 24px;
      }
      
      .footer-logo {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 10px;
          color: var(--primary);
          font-weight: 700;
          font-size: 20px;
      }
      
      .footer-links {
          display: flex;
          gap: 24px;
      }
      
      .footer-link {
          color: var(--text-light);
          text-decoration: none;
          transition: var(--transition);
      }
      
      .footer-link:hover {
          color: var(--primary);
      }
      
      .copyright {
          color: var(--text-light);
          font-size: 14px;
      }
      
      /* Responsive */
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
          .hero h1 {
              font-size: 28px;
          }
          
          .hero p {
              font-size: 16px;
          }
          
          .workflow-steps {
              gap: 15px;
          }
          
          .step {
              max-width: 120px;
          }
          
          .step-text {
              font-size: 12px;
          }
          
          .cards-grid {
              grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          }
          
          .footer-links {
              flex-direction: column;
              gap: 12px;
              text-align: center;
          }
      }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
      <div class="container">
          <div class="header-content">
              <div class="logo">
                  <i class="fas fa-seedling logo-icon"></i>
                  <div>
                      <div class="logo-text">SmartAgro</div>
                      <div class="logo-subtitle">Blockchain Intelligence para o Agronegócio</div>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="user-info">
                  <div class="user-avatar">JS</div>
                  <div>João Silva</div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
  </header>
  
  <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
          <div class="hero-content">
              <h1>Análise de Viabilidade Blockchain</h1>
              <p>Calcule custos de implementação e simule a adoção de contratos inteligentes no agronegócio brasileiro</p>
              
              <div class="workflow-steps">
                  <div class="step">
                      <div class="step-number">1</div>
                      <div class="step-text">Analise dados do Censo Agropecuário</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="step">
                      <div class="step-number">2</div>
                      <div class="step-text">Implemente contratos inteligentes</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="step">
                      <div class="step-number">3</div>
                      <div class="step-text">Calcule custos de transação</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="step">
                      <div class="step-number">4</div>
                      <div class="step-text">Simule adoção em larga escala</div>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="cards-section">
      <div class="container">
          <h2 class="section-title">Ferramentas de Análise</h2>
          <div class="cards-grid">
              <div class="card card-1" onclick="location.href='/dashboard'">
                  <div class="card-icon">
                      <i class="fas fa-database"></i>
                  </div>
                  <div class="card-content">
                      <h3 class="card-title">Indicadores IBGE</h3>
                      <p class="card-description">Acesse dados do Censo Agropecuário com visualizações interativas de estabelecimentos e comercialização por produto.</p>
                      <button class="card-button">
                          <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i> Explorar Dados
                      </button>
                  </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card card-2" onclick="location.href='/interface'">
                  <div class="card-icon">
                      <i class="fas fa-file-contract"></i>
                  </div>
                  <div class="card-content">
                      <h3 class="card-title">Implementar Contratos</h3>
                      <p class="card-description">Faça upload, compile e implemente contratos inteligentes com modos automático ou iterativo para testes detalhados.</p>
                      <button class="card-button">
                          <i class="fas fa-upload"></i> Implementar
                      </button>
                  </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card card-3" onclick="location.href='/gas'">
                  <div class="card-icon">
                      <i class="fas fa-calculator"></i>
                  </div>
                  <div class="card-content">
                      <h3 class="card-title">Cálculo de Custos</h3>
                      <p class="card-description">Analise consumo de gas, custos por rede blockchain e cotações atualizadas em tempo real.</p>
                      <button class="card-button">
                          <i class="fas fa-gas-pump"></i> Calcular Custos
                      </button>
                  </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card card-4" onclick="location.href='/results'">
                  <div class="card-icon">
                      <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                  </div>
                  <div class="card-content">
                      <h3 class="card-title">Simulação de Adoção</h3>
                      <p class="card-description">Cruze custos blockchain com dados do IBGE para projetar viabilidade em diferentes cenários de adoção.</p>
                      <button class="card-button">
                          <i class="fas fa-project-diagram"></i> Simular Cenários
                      </button>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
  </section>
  
  <footer>
      <div class="container">
          <div class="footer-content">
              <div class="footer-logo">
                  <i class="fas fa-seedling"></i>
                  <span>SmartAgro</span>
              </div>
              <div class="footer-links">
                  <a href="#" class="footer-link">Sobre Nós</a>
                  <a href="#" class="footer-link">Contato</a>
                  <a href="#" class="footer-link">Documentação</a>
                  <a href="#" class="footer-link">Termos de Uso</a>
              </div>
              <div class="copyright">
                  &copy; 2023 SmartAgro. Dados do Censo Agropecuário IBGE.
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
